Steps to fetch data via Retrofit library
1.Add retrofit as dependency
2.Create data class to serialize data
    points:  @SerializedName("userId") @Expose var userId:Int,
3.Create Dao interface
    points: Call<T> and @GET ,@POST annotation
    ! @FormUrlEncoded annotation
4.Create retrofit client
5.Create ApiUtils and implement Dao interface getter function with using retrofit client
6.Call ApiUtils.getUsersDao() methode and reach the interface then implement enqueue function and callbacks